## How to use this template

For a new client repo:

```bash
cd <client-repo>
cat /path/to/agent-stack/config/CLAUDE.md.template >> CLAUDE.md
$EDITOR CLAUDE.md
# Trim the comment header, customize the project-specific quality bar
git add CLAUDE.md
git commit -m "Add agent-stack engineering rituals to CLAUDE.md"
```
